Stephen Rivera (1946-) was adopted in Kansas City, United States on September 17th, 1946. His Biological mother said he was just too "stinky". His mothers name is Brittany Rivera, a trucker (1900-). His father name is Jeremiah Rivera, a restaurant owner (1899-) and has a brother named Trayvon (1939-) The family has a pussycat named Theo. 

