At age 5, he started Wildcat Elementary school, and developed the flu. At age 6, one of his classmates Boomer Tweedy, just tried to start a game, hot potato in the middle of class with another student in the middle of a lesson. He ignored his antics. At age 8, one of his old neighbors down the block was having a yard sale, and he decided to visit, he decided to purchase the vintage action figure. At age 9, he got bullied by a classmate named Keenan ross, he told his big brother, he banged his lips. At age 10, one of his other classmates, Adrian Kovacic just began jumping from desk-to-desk in his teacher, Mrs. McCormick's, class, he chose to ignore it.